      "text": [
        " اَلرَّبِيثَا فَمَا تَأْمُرُنِي فِيهَا فَكَتَبَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ \"لاَ بَأْسَ بِهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4204 - Muhammad ibn Isma'il ibn Bazi' wrote to Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as), saying:\n\"The people have differed regarding the rabbit (al-rabitha). What do you command me concerning it?\"\nImam (as) wrote back: \"There is no harm in it.\""
        ]
      }
    },
